
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sistema de Carimbos - TLP</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap');

        :root {
            /* Cores TLP Oficiais */
            --tlp-orange: #E85D1F;
            --tlp-orange-dark: #C74D15;
            --tlp-orange-light: #FF7A3D;
            --tlp-yellow: #F5A623;
            --tlp-yellow-light: #FFB84D;
            --success-color: #10b981;
            --warning-color: #f59e0b;
            --danger-color: #ef4444;
            
            /* Tema Claro */
            --bg-primary: #ffffff;
            --bg-secondary: #FFF8F3;
            --bg-tertiary: #FFE8DC;
            --text-primary: #2D1810;
            --text-secondary: #8B4513;
            --border-color: #FFD4BA;
            --shadow: rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.15);
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --input-bg: #ffffff;
            --accent-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #E85D1F 0%, #F5A623 100%);
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] {
            --bg-primary: #1a0f0a;
            --bg-secondary: #2d1810;
            --bg-tertiary: #3d2418;
            --text-primary: #fff8f3;
            --text-secondary: #ffb88c;
            --border-color: #4d3020;
            --shadow: rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.3);
            --card-bg: #2d1810;
            --input-bg: #3d2418;
            --accent-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #E85D1F 0%, #F5A623 100%);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .top-bar {
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            padding: 1.2rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.3);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .logo-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.2rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            padding: 0.6rem 1.8rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 55px;
            height: 55px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e88e1f 0%, #ffb237 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            position: relative;
        }

        .logo-icon::before {
            content: 'TLP';
            position: absolute;
            background: white;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .logo-text {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo-text .company-name {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            line-height: 1;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .logo-text .company-subtitle {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            opacity: 0.95;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .theme-toggle {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.7rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: white;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .theme-toggle:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .theme-toggle i {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .page-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.3);
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .page-header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: pulse 15s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0.5; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(180deg); opacity: 0.8; }
        }

        .page-header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .page-header p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            opacity: 0.95;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .navigation {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .nav-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 3px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 3rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .nav-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.3);
            border-color: var(--tlp-orange);
        }

        .nav-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 0.08;
        }

        .nav-card-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .nav-card h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--tlp-orange);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .nav-card p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .nav-card .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.3rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-top: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.3);
        }

        .page-content {
            display: none;
        }

        .page-content.active {
            display: block;
            animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .back-button {
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 1rem 2.2rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.3);
        }

        .back-button:hover {
            transform: translateX(-5px) scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.4);
        }

        .toolbar {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 1.8rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 1.2rem;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px var(--shadow);
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .toolbar button {
            padding: 0.95rem 2rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.7rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-success:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-warning:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4);
        }

        .search-box {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 280px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .search-box i {
            position: absolute;
            left: 1.2rem;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: var(--tlp-orange);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .search-box input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.95rem 1.2rem 0.95rem 3.2rem;
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            background: var(--input-bg);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .search-box input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--tlp-orange);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.1);
        }

        .filters {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .filter-btn {
            padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            background: var(--card-bg);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            border-radius: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .filter-btn:hover {
            border-color: var(--tlp-orange);
            color: var(--tlp-orange);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .filter-btn.active {
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            color: white;
            border-color: var(--tlp-orange);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.3);
        }

        .stamps-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(400px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }

        .stamp-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px var(--shadow);
        }

        .stamp-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.2);
            border-color: var(--tlp-orange);
        }

        .stamp-header {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .stamp-body {
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .stamp-field {
            margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
            padding: 1.3rem;
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--tlp-orange);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .stamp-field:hover {
            background: var(--bg-tertiary);
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        .stamp-field label {
            display: block;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--tlp-orange);
            margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .stamp-field input,
        .stamp-field textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.95rem;
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: var(--input-bg);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .stamp-field input:focus,
        .stamp-field textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--tlp-orange);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.1);
        }

        .stamp-field textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 100px;
        }

        .stamp-actions {
            padding: 1.3rem 2rem;
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.2rem;
            border-top: 2px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .stamp-actions button {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 0.95rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .btn-copy {
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-copy:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-clear {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-clear:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-delete {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-delete:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
        }

        /* Cores dos carimbos TLP */
        .color-yellow { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F5A623 0%, #FFB84D 100%); }
        .color-blue { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E85D1F 0%, #F5A623 100%); }
        .color-black { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C74D15 0%, #E85D1F 100%); }
        .color-orange { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E85D1F 0%, #FF7A3D 100%); }
        .color-green { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%); }
        .color-purple { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #7c3aed 100%); }
        .color-red { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%); }

        .notification {
            position: fixed;
            top: 100px;
            right: 20px;
            padding: 1.3rem 2rem;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 3px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px var(--shadow);
            z-index: 2000;
            display: none;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            animation: slideIn 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            max-width: 450px;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .notification.show {
            display: flex;
        }

        .notification.success {
            border-color: var(--success-color);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1) 0%, rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.1) 100%);
        }

        .notification.error {
            border-color: var(--danger-color);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1) 0%, rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.1) 100%);
        }

        .notification i {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .notification.success i {
            color: var(--success-color);
        }

        .notification.error i {
            color: var(--danger-color);
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                transform: translateX(500px);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                transform: translateX(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        .stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.3);
            color: white;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .stat-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(232, 93, 31, 0.4);
        }

        .stat-card h3 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            font-weight: 800;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .stat-card p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            opacity: 0.95;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            .stamps-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .toolbar {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .search-box {
                width: 100%;
            }

            .page-header h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .logo-text .company-name {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .nav-card {
                padding: 2.5rem;
            }

            .navigation {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .stamp-actions {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }

        .empty-state {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 5rem 2rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .empty-state-icon {
            font-size: 6rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.4;
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .empty-state h3 {
            color: var(--tlp-orange);
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .empty-state p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="top-bar">
        <div class="logo-section">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <div class="logo-icon">TLP</div>
                <div class="logo-text">
                    <span class="company-name">TLP</span>
                    <span class="company-subtitle">CONECTADOS COM O FUTURO</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="theme-toggle" onclick="toggleTheme()">
            <i class="fas fa-moon" id="themeIcon"></i>
            <span id="themeText">Tema Escuro</span>
        </button>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- Página Inicial -->
        <div id="homePage" class="page-content active">
            <div class="page-header">
                <h1>Sistema de Carimbos TLP</h1>
                <p>Plataforma Corporativa de Gerenciamento de Carimbos</p>
            </div>

            <div class="navigation">
                <div class="nav-card" onclick="showPage('cscPage')">
                    <div class="nav-card-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-building"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h2>Carimbos CSC/CCI</h2>
                    <p>Acesse os carimbos específicos do CSC/CCI com todos os campos padronizados para operações técnicas</p>
                    <span class="badge">
                        <i class="fas fa-stamp"></i>
                        18 Carimbos Disponíveis
                    </span>
                </div>

                <div class="nav-card" onclick="showPage('padraoPage')">
                    <div class="nav-card-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h2>Carimbos Padrão</h2>
                    <p>Utilize os carimbos padrão para operações comuns e rotinas do dia a dia operacional</p>
                    <span class="badge">
                        <i class="fas fa-stamp"></i>
                        5 Carimbos Disponíveis
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Página Carimbos CSC -->
        <div id="cscPage" class="page-content">
            <button class="back-button" onclick="showPage('homePage')">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
                Voltar ao Início
            </button>
            
            <div class="page-header">
                <h1>Carimbos CSC/CCI</h1>
                <p>Carimbos específicos para operações do Centro de Serviços Compartilhados</p>
